text: Tanduay Rhum is an alcoholic drink from the Philippines. It is produced by Tanduay Distillers Inc., and with origins dating from 1854. ==References== ==Other websites== *Tanduay's official website Category:1854 establishments Category:Alcoholic spirits Category:Companies of the Philippines Category:1850s establishments in Asia Category:19th-century establishments in the Philippines
